OL,3,CBBC 'let down' over scandals involving
OL,4,Chigh-profile staff and shows
OL,6,FThe BBC has been "let down" by several
OL,7,Fcontroversies which have rocked the
OL,8,Fbroadcaster in recent months involving
OL,9,Fhigh-profile presenters and TV shows,
OL,10,Fdirector-general Tim Davie said.
OL,12,FDavie said the broadcaster has been
OL,13,Fput in the "spotlight" following
OL,14,Fallegations surrounding treatment of
OL,15,Fcontestants on Strictly Come Dancing
OL,16,Fand the sacking of Jermaine Jenas
OL,17,Fafter he admitted sending
OL,18,Finappropriate messages to female
OL,19,Fcolleagues.
