OL,3,CBBC 'let down' over scandals involving
OL,4,Chigh-profile staff and shows
OL,6,FIt comes after the BBC called for Huw
OL,7,FEdwards to return his estimated
OL,8,F#200,000 salary he was paid between
OL,9,Fhis arrest and pleading guilty to
OL,10,Fmaking indecent images of children,
OL,11,Ffor which he is awaiting sentencing.
OL,13,FIn an email to BBC staff on Wednesday
OL,14,Fafternoon, seen by the PA news agency,
OL,15,FMr Davie said he wanted to acknowledge
OL,16,F"this has been a demanding period for
OL,17,Fthe BBC and everyone who works within
OL,18,Fit".
