OL,3,CBBC 'let down' over scandals involving
OL,4,Chigh-profile staff and shows
OL,6,F"The shocking news about Huw Edwards,
OL,7,Fand other stories concerning some of
OL,8,Four high-profile shows, have put the
OL,9,FBBC in the spotlight," the 57-year-old
OL,10,Fwrote.
OL,12,F"It can be challenging for us all when
OL,13,Fthe BBC becomes the headline. We work
OL,14,Ffor this wonderful organisation
OL,15,Fbecause we care about what it stands
OL,16,Ffor and the role it plays in society.
OL,18,F"I know we have all felt let down and
OL,19,Fworried about the impact on the BBC.
