OL,3,CBBC 'let down' over scandals involving
OL,4,Chigh-profile staff and shows
OL,6,F"Personally, on my watch, building a
OL,7,Fpositive culture and making the BBC a
OL,8,Fgreat place to work is a critical
OL,9,Fpriority," he added.
OL,11,F"I know that many people are proud of
OL,12,Ftheir teams and feel they are working
OL,13,Fin a supportive and positive
OL,14,Fenvironment. We must make that
OL,15,Funiversal."
OL,17,FThe email comes a week after it was
OL,18,Frevealed Match Of The Day and The One
OL,19,FShow host Jenas had been sacked from
OL,20,Fthe BBC.
