OL,4,Chigh-profile staff and shows
OL,6,FThe 41-year-old apologised for sending
OL,7,Finappropriate messages to two female
OL,8,Fmembers of staff but insisted they
OL,9,Fwere "between two consenting adults"
OL,10,Fand that his behaviour was not illegal.
OL,12,FIt marked the latest blow to the BBC
OL,13,Fafter Edwards' child abuse scandal and
OL,14,Fbullying allegations on Strictly Come
OL,15,FDancing.
